{"tid":2366843,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"路透稱小米被列入涉嫌與中國軍方有關聯企業的黑名單","createTime":"2021-01-15T01:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T02:44:34.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"785be2adc8918647c1a48ca196d9c1410aaaf673","tid":2366843,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"路透社引述文件報道，美國特朗普政府將9間中國企業，列入涉嫌與中國軍方有關聯企業的黑名單，包括手機製造商小米，以及飛機製造商中國商用飛機。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，這些企業將受到一項新的美國投資禁令約束，禁令要求美國投資者在今年11月11日後，不能夠再持有這些企業的股份。<br />\n<br />\n有華府高層官員早前說，新的行政命令確保美國保留關鍵工具，保障美國投資者免於資助中國軍事現代化。"},{"pid":"83333191f4effcc5663fc7f565fdaf49c17904ba","tid":2366843,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb1ad0ef3adab00fd4bfc5424a4134a511dcd27","tid":2366843,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">小米大幅低開11%</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570535-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570535-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=72a95c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570535-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=58367d85\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570535-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n小米低開11%，報29元，外電報道，美國政府將小米等9家中國企業，列入涉嫌與中國軍方有關聯企業的黑名單。"}]}